dc_title_s: Brazil--north coast, Salinópolis to Baixo do Espadarte (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: from Brazilian Navy surveys to 1980, with additions and corrections to 1984. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by hachures. "Soundings in meters." "Reproduction of Brazilian Chart 302, 3rd edition, Dec. 27, 1983 with modifications in accordance with the Brazilian Directorate of Hydrography and Navigation. Brazilian copyright law applies." This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA). United States. Diretoria de Hidrografia e Navegação. Defense Mapping Agency. (1986). Brazil--north coast, Salinópolis to Baixo do Espadarte (Raster Image). LandInfo. Available at: https://purl.stanford.edu/cd933ng0893 This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
dc_creator_sm: United States. Diretoria de Hidrografia e Navegação. Defense Mapping Agency
